title: San Francisco/The Avenues
name: S&E Cafe
directions: between Taraval St and Ulloa St
price: $7-14 for complete dinners; $3-7 apps and other dishes; $2-4 for beverages
content: Midwestern American food as seen through Hong Kong eyes: complete meals include soup, roll, coffee or HK milk tea, entree, rice or spaghetti, Jello or Chinese bean soup dessert. Extensive list of unusual beverages from Ovaltine to Ginger Coke to green tea milk shakes; Chinese food available after 10PM only. Coffee shop ambiance with TVs at low volume usually tuned to a Chinese station.
